{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7ac380b9ea","title":"北京军区某毛泽东思想学习班天津班一日生活毛泽东思想化的具体做法","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7c26bf684b","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"7ac380b9ea"}],"tags":[{"id":"145a049082","name":"天津文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fe5a99cb42","type":"title","text":"北京军区某毛泽东思想学习班天津班一日生活毛泽东思想化的具体做法","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"2078c591a5","type":"subtitle","text":"翻印者按：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"86acb1b04f","type":"paragraph","text":"为了把“三忠于”活动在全厂范围内迅速、广泛、深入、持久地开展起来;为了促进思想忠字化，工作忠字化，生活忠字化。本期我们特将《北京军区第三篇地干毛泽东思想学习班天津班一日生活毛泽东思想化的具体做法》介绍于下，供同志们学习参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"b3128240dd","type":"paragraph","text":"经我班全体学员研究实践落实到一日生活毛泽东思想化，具体做法如下：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"15ae2577e5","type":"subtitle","text":"(一)每天坚持做到四“第一”","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"3b95707fd7","type":"paragraph","text":"第一句话：毛主席万岁!(起床后)","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"64d7b83555","type":"paragraph","text":"第一件事：向毛主席祝愿。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"6db89d153c","type":"paragraph","text":"第一支歌：唱《东方红》。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"6221be01a7","type":"paragraph","text":"第一堂课：读毛主席的书。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"6990af704c","type":"subtitle","text":"(二)向毛主席请示：","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"01107c40d3","type":"paragraph","text":"1、向伟大领袖毛主席敬礼。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"e50deb2fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"2、齐声高唱《东方红》。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"cdb5e1108a","type":"paragraph","text":"3、共同敬祝我们心中最红最红的红太阳、最最敬爱的伟大领袖毛主席万寿无疆!万寿无疆!万寿无疆!","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"7df2fd5de9","type":"paragraph","text":"敬祝我们的林副统帅身体健康!永远健康!永远健康!","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"d6dc7203f3","type":"paragraph","text":"4、向伟大领袖毛主席宣誓：(誓词：我们要一辈子读您的书，听您的话，照您的指示办事。誓死保卫您，誓死保卫您的伟大思想，誓死保卫您的无产阶级革命路线。誓做一个忠于党，忠于您老人家，忠于人民的红色战士。)","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"bff94721d1","type":"paragraph","text":"5、学习最高指示。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"32d19686c6","type":"subtitle","text":"(三)天天读：","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"b6a0cd0dd7","type":"paragraph","text":"每天八——九点天天读，主要读老五篇，以个人阅读为主，带着问题学，活学活用，学用结合，急用先学，立竿见影，在用字上狠下功夫。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"a2c9f40323","type":"subtitle","text":"(四)三前(上班、开会、吃饭)做到三不忘：即不忘向毛主席祝愿，不忘学习最高指示，不忘唱《东方红》或者其他革命歌曲(天大地大不如党的恩情大、大海航行靠舵手等等)。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"79476a70c5","type":"subtitle","text":"(五)时时、处处、事事用毛泽东思想挂帅，做到四个不离：即手不离毛主席的书，口不离毛主席的话，心不离毛主席的指示，行动不离毛主席的教导。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"8703935b2a","type":"paragraph","text":"1、小组学习讨论时，个人要选用有针对性语录来指导自己的思想，用毛主席的话来说明问题，活学活用。","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"44ca9b7ab9","type":"paragraph","text":"2、同志互相谈心，互相帮助，互赠语录。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"8a95fe82c7","type":"paragraph","text":"3、打电话第一句话要说：祝毛主席万寿无疆或读最高指示。","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"68aa5cb820","type":"subtitle","text":"(六)集体队列生活革命化：","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"2e283593f2","type":"paragraph","text":"口令：","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"bf758c6ee5","type":"paragraph","text":"集合：召之即来!","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"e6a08ae475","type":"paragraph","text":"立正：毛主席万岁!万岁!万岁!万岁!万岁!","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"d8b8f07f5a","type":"paragraph","text":"向右看齐：打到刘、邓、陶!","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"0d2ea9a165","type":"paragraph","text":"向前看：胸怀祖国，放眼世界。","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"4bdb958695","type":"paragraph","text":"向右转：“要斗私批修”。","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"ee183ec115","type":"paragraph","text":"向左看：向林副主席学习。","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"4ed8c218d8","type":"paragraph","text":"起步走：紧跟毛主席，永远干革命。","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"68c035cb48","type":"paragraph","text":"稍息：提高警惕。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"8a4c350d1a","type":"paragraph","text":"解散：加强纪律性，革命无不胜。","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"3e645b0765","type":"paragraph","text":"行进间：口号：","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"755101eb65","type":"paragraph","text":"1、伟大的导师、伟大的领袖、伟大的统帅、伟大的舵手毛主席万万岁!万岁!万岁!万岁!","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"b0dd1d6c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"2、下定决心，不怕牺牲，排除万难，去争取胜利。(可重复)","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"6d8992077d","type":"paragraph","text":"3、团结、紧张、严肃、活泼。","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"f33c449941","type":"subtitle","text":"(七)向毛主席汇报(下班前)","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"e2095e1041","type":"paragraph","text":"1、向毛主席敬礼。","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"c11e4ecc47","type":"paragraph","text":"2、向毛主席和林副主席祝愿。","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"f4f610124c","type":"paragraph","text":"3、学习最高指示。","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"0c597516c4","type":"paragraph","text":"4、个人汇报(一天的思想革命化的经验、教训、体会)。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"7636710446","type":"paragraph","text":"5、唱《大海航行靠舵手》。","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"},{"id":"eaa8b2adf2","type":"paragraph","text":" 杭州发电设备厂革命造反联合总司令部政宣组翻印1968年5月19日","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea"}],"page":{"id":"b300e91e20","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ac380b9ea","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}